    "Soundpost": {
      "shouldTranslate": false
    },
    "Soundpost Pro": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpost Pro"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpost Pro"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Soundpost Pro is active": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpost Pro 有効"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpost Pro 已启用"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Soundpost Pro is active — thank you.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpost Pro が有効です — ありがとうございます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpost Pro 已启用 — 谢谢你。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Soundpost can tag each capsule with the place it was recorded — a memory of where, not just when. Tap Continue to choose whether to allow location.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpostは録音した場所をカプセルに記録できます——「いつ」だけでなく「どこで」も。「続ける」をタップすると、位置情報を許可するか選べます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpost 可以为每枚胶囊记下录音地点——不只是何时，还有何地。点按“继续”即可选择是否允许定位。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Soundpost is free — capture, seal, resurface, back up to iCloud, and receive every memory. Pro adds richer ways to make and share them.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpost は無料です — 録音、封印、再会、iCloud バックアップ、そしてすべての思い出を受け取ること。Pro は、思い出をより豊かに作り、共有する方法を加えます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpost 是免费的 — 录制、封存、重逢、备份到 iCloud，以及接收每一段回忆。Pro 让你以更丰富的方式创作和分享它们。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Soundpost is free — capture, seal, resurface, back up, and receive every memory. Pro adds richer ways to make and share them, and never locks a memory.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpostは無料です——録音、封印、再浮上、バックアップ、そしてすべての思い出を受け取れます。Proはより豊かな作成・共有を加えますが、思い出をロックすることはありません。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpost 是免费的——录制、封存、重现、备份并接收每一段记忆。Pro 增添更丰富的制作与分享方式，且永不锁住任何记忆。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Soundpost will hide this capsule and notify you on %@. This is a gentle, honor-system seal kept on your device — not encryption.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpost はこのカプセルを非表示にし、%@にお知らせします。これは端末上のやさしい善意の封印で、暗号化ではありません。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpost 会隐藏这个胶囊，并在 %@ 通知你。这是设备上温柔、基于自觉的封印，并非加密。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Start recording": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "録音を開始"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "开始录音"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Stop recording": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "録音を停止"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "停止录音"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Subscribe": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "登録する"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "订阅"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tag where I am": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "現在地を追加"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "标记当前位置"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tender": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "やさしい"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "温柔"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Terms of Use": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "利用規約"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "使用条款"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "That recording was too short. Try holding a moment longer.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "録音が短すぎました。もう少し長めに録音してみてください。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "录音太短了，请按住再多录一会儿。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The annual plan auto-renews each year until you cancel. Manage or cancel anytime in your App Store account settings, at least 24 hours before the renewal date. Payment is charged to your Apple Account at confirmation. Lifetime is a one-time purchase. Your existing and received memories are never locked.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "年額プランは、解約するまで毎年自動更新されます。更新日の少なくとも24時間前までに、App Store のアカウント設定でいつでも管理・解約できます。お支払いは確定時に Apple アカウントへ請求されます。買い切りは一度きりの購入です。すでにある思い出や受け取った思い出が、ロックされることはありません。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "年付方案在你取消前每年自动续订。你可以在续订日期前至少 24 小时，随时在 App Store 账户设置中管理或取消。确认购买时将向你的 Apple 账户收费。终身买断为一次性购买。你已有的和已收到的回忆绝不会被锁住。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The old train crossing bell": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "懐かしい踏切の音"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "老式道口的铃声"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This bundles %@ of audio plus a manifest of your notes, moods, places and dates. It's your own data — nothing new leaves your device.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "音声約%@と、メモ・気分・場所・日付の一覧をまとめます。あなた自身のデータで、新たに端末の外に出るものはありません。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这会打包约 %@ 的音频，以及你的笔记、心情、地点和日期清单。这是你自己的数据——没有新内容离开你的设备。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This capsule is sealed and will reappear here on its date. To be reminded on the day, turn on notifications for Soundpost in Settings.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このカプセルは封印され、指定の日付にここで再び現れます。当日にお知らせを受け取るには、設定でSoundpostの通知をオンにしてください。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这枚胶囊已封存，会在设定的日期重新出现在这里。若想在当天收到提醒，请在“设置”中开启 Soundpost 的通知。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This capsule opens %@.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "このカプセルは%@に開きます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这个胶囊将于 %@ 开启。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This month": {
      "comment": "Gallery date section header",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今月"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "本月"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This permanently removes the recording.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "録音が完全に削除されます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这将永久删除录音。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This removes the reminder schedule and device tokens Soundpost keeps on its server. Your capsules stay on this device and in iCloud. Far-future reminders fall back to this device's local schedule.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Soundpost がサーバーに保存しているリマインダーのスケジュールとデバイストークンを削除します。カプセルはこの端末と iCloud に残ります。遠い未来のリマインダーは、この端末のローカルスケジュールに切り替わります。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "这会删除 Soundpost 保存在服务器上的提醒计划和设备令牌。你的胶囊仍保留在本机和 iCloud 中。远期提醒将回退到本机的本地计划。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tinted": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ティント"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "淡彩"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Try again": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "もう一度試す"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "重试"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Ueno Park": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "上野公園"
          }
